data.description: Custom home with all of the bells & whistles. Located on a private corner lot in the La Contenta golf course community in Valley Springs. If you love to entertain this home is an ideal set up for family gatherings, holiday parties and fun summer BBQ's. As you arrive you will be impressed with the curb appeal, 3 car garage, matured landscape and all the space for parking. Step inside and fall in love with this welcoming floorplan with a formal entry way that opens to a spacious family room with high ceilings, built ins and crown molding, make your way to the custom kitchen with granite counters, large island, stainless appliances and sunny breakfast nook that overlooks the back yard oasis, plus oversized mudroom, office/bonus room, 2 guest rooms, master suite with large walk-in closet, master bath with soaking tub, then make your way out to the back deck and enjoy your morning coffee and the gorgeous views. Take a few steps down and hop into the inground pool or sit on the patio and relax after a long day or even better invite some guests over and play a game of pool or watch the football game in the large fully functional game room with granite bar top, fridge, dish washer, half bath or use this space as an in-law quarters it has private access and ample storage plus there is a work shop and golf cart garage, this home really has it all and its close to several amenities, it's really a must see!
